The paper discusses Bayesian neural learning, which is a topic that falls under machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of Markov chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) techniques and parallel tempering suggests that the paper may fall under the category of computational statistics (cs.ST) or machine learning (cs.LG). However, the focus on neural networks and the applications in time series prediction and pattern classification suggest that the paper is more likely to be categorized under cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, or cs.CV.
